ntent, sequence_id, client_message_id, created_at }`\n  - `message:read_receipt`
— Payload: `{ conversation_id, last_read_message_id }`\n  - `conversation:update
d` — Payload: `{ conversation_id, updated_at }`\n  - `message:error` — Payload: 
